    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/about_me/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/about_me/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure class=&#34;wrap-right-award&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img&#xA;          class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;          loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;          decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;          fetchpriority=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;          alt=&#34;me&#34;&#xA;          width=&#34;1828&#34;&#xA;          height=&#34;2619&#34;&#xA;          src=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/rainbow_hu_374df01dfa4857fb.jpg&#34;&#xA;          srcset=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/rainbow_hu_374df01dfa4857fb.jpg 800w,/img/rainbow_hu_fc6fbeba5789eb80.jpg 1280w&#34;&#xA;          sizes=&#34;(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 65vw&#34;&#xA;          data-zoom-src=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/rainbow.jpg&#34;&#xA;        /&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who am I?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-am-i&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-am-i&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I am a Research Fellow in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.unisq.edu.au/research/institutes-centres/iaess/centre-for-astrophysics&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Centre for Astrophysics&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.unisq.edu.au/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;University of Southern Queensland&lt;/a&gt;. I am based, however, in Sydney where I hold honorary appointments at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://sifa.sydney.edu.au/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;University of Sydney&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mq.edu.au/research/research-centres-groups-and-facilities/centres/astrophysics-and-space-technologies&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Macquarie University&lt;/a&gt;. Throughout the week you can usually find me at SIfA on Mondays, Macquarie on Fridays, and working from home the rest of the week. I&amp;rsquo;m usually on UniSQ campus once a month, so if you need to see me in person just let me know and we can coordinate.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/art_about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/art_about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;UniSQ&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;3799&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;1182&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art_all_hu_46b5df2958ec4cdc.png&#34;&#xA;    srcset=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art_all_hu_46b5df2958ec4cdc.png 800w, https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art_all_hu_3da9a9280a20168d.png 1280w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 65vw&#34;&#xA;    data-zoom-src=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art_all.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Art has been a lifelong hobby of mine. I have always loved to draw and paint. Recently I have been drawing astronomical observatories, some of which are shown above. Want a drawing of your telescope? Shoot me an &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:rebecca.mcelroy@unisq.edu.au&#34; &gt;email&lt;/a&gt; or a DM on &lt;a href=&#34;instagram.com/paintingbybex&#34; &gt;instagram&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&#34;twitter.com/re_mcelroy&#34; &gt;twitter&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I also do a lot of portaiture of characters from TV and video games, and make stickers on &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.redbubble.com/people/paintingbybex/shop&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;redbubble&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
