    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/sci_art/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/sci_art/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;Art&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;3824&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;1510&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art_hu_bb3aea63363a21cc.png&#34;&#xA;    srcset=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art_hu_bb3aea63363a21cc.png 800w, https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art_hu_a6ce87a4d1e2dd12.png 1280w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 65vw&#34;&#xA;    data-zoom-src=&#34;https://rebeccamcelroy.github.io/img/art.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Science illustration combines my two passions. I started out doing simple drawings for talks and have recently been illustrating astronomical observatories. You can find my work on &lt;a href=&#34;instagram.com/paintingbybex&#34; &gt;instagram&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;twitter.com/re_mcelroy&#34; &gt;twitter&lt;/a&gt;, and even &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.redbubble.com/people/paintingbybex/shop&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;redbubble&lt;/a&gt; if you would like a sticker or mug.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;On &lt;a href=&#34;https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1C8KAJDvMLDopVWPV1iUUh7cJ2aeBp6G4?usp=sharing&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;this site&lt;/a&gt; you can find my various illustrations, which are free for you to use with attribution. Enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
